title: Jhin Q Sound Effect Bug
body: Sometimes when im in game as Jhin vs a Karma/Jayce, when I press Q the 2nd,3rd, and 4th bounces play the sound effect from karmas Q or jayce's ability(i dont remember which) im not sure if it has to be enemy or ally.
